vcpu:
  virtual cpu. instructions are 16-bit.

note:
  this is an old project.  the vcpu works but should be redesigned.
  assembler is currently incomplete and broken.

registers:
  there are 8 registers, r0 to r7.

opcodes:
  let a and b refer to registers
  add: 0x00ab
  sub: 0x10ab
  mul: 0x20ab
  div: 0x30ab
  jmp: 0x40nn
  set: 0x5ann
  mov: 0x60ab

